## Primary Overnight

**Rising 2nd-3rd Graders**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Primary Camp"] /%}

A fun first taste of overnight camp just for our youngest campers! Primary Overnight lets our campers experience camp games, cabin time, and community all in an action packed introduction to the Bear Lake Camp experience.

{% ctaButton
