## Junior Camp

**Rising 3rd-5th or 4th-6th Graders**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Junior 1", "Junior 2", "Junior 3"] /%}

Full-week adventure for elementary students! Junior Campers enjoy a full schedule of activities — Worship, Bible Study, games (like Melee), waterfront fun, crafts, campfires, and more — all while building mentor relationships and friendships.

{% ctaButton
   label="Register Now"
   href="https://www.ultracamp.com/clientlogin.aspx?idCamp=268&campCode=blc"
   variant="inverse"
   size="lg"
   textColor="accent" /%}
{% /gridSquare %}

