## Jr. High Camp

**Rising 7th-9th Graders**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Jr. High 1", "Jr. High 2", "Jr. High 3"] /%}

A week of growth and exploration for middle school students! Jr. High Campers get challenged to grow in their faith through group discussions, Inductive Bible Studies, and Chapel Messages, all while experiencing exciting activities and building lasting friendships.

{% ctaButton
   label="Register Now"
   href="https://www.ultracamp.com/clientlogin.aspx?idCamp=268&campCode=blc"
   variant="inverse"
   size="lg"
   textColor="secondary" /%}
{% /gridSquare %}

