## Sr. High Camp

**Rising 10th Graders - Graduates**

{% sessionCapacity sessions=["Sr. High"] /%}

Our summer session for high school students! Sr. High campers dive into rich community, awesome activities like black light dodgeball and a Square Dance Night, and are equipped to engage Jesus Christ through Scripture and Worship.

{% ctaButton
   label="Register Now"
   href="https://www.ultracamp.com/clientlogin.aspx?idCamp=268&campCode=blc"
