## Registration Information

{% cardGrid cols="2" width="auto" height="auto" %}
{% contentCard
   icon="DollarSign"
   iconSize="md"
   title="Pricing & Early Bird"
   headingLevel="3"
   width="auto"
   height="auto" %}
Primary Overnight: $100 | All Other Sessions: $390 through 4/13, $440 after 4/13

Early bird pricing available for registrations completed by April 13, 2026.
{% /contentCard %}

{% contentCard
   icon="Heart"
   iconSize="md"
   title="Share the Love Discount"
   headingLevel="3"
   width="auto"
   height="auto" %}
**$50 off** your week of camp for every first time camper who attends the same week because of your invitation.

Applied upon arrival at session check-in.
{% /contentCard %}

{% contentCard
   icon="GraduationCap"
   iconSize="md"
   title="Grade Levels"
   headingLevel="3"
   width="auto"
   height="auto" %}
